attributes.long-description:
Download the Interstellar Bundle for Super Stardust Delta and receive the Super Stardust Delta Full Game, along with all four extra modes contained in the Blast Pack - Endless Mode, Impact Mode, Bomber Mode, and Twin Gun Mode. This is the ultimate Super Stardust Experience.

Download it today!

Game Description:

The Super Stardust franchise blasts its way into your hands with its latest iteration: Super Stardust Delta. With brand-new features made specifically for PlayStation®Vita, players continue to destroy everything in their sight. Create black holes, launch swarm missiles and unleash shockwaves with all-new PlayStation®Vita controls.

Key Features.
o Precise Twin Stick controls.
o New controls, mechanics and enemies designed specifically for PlayStation®Vita.
o All modes from Super Stardust HD and Super Stardust Portable plus new modes and challenges for PlayStation®Vita.

Purchase or use of this item is subject to the PlayStation®Network Terms of Service, this item’s use restrictions, and other applicable terms located at http://www.us.playstation.com/support/useragreements. If you do not wish to accept all these terms, do not purchase or use this item. One-time fee for downloads to up to two systems that are associated with the purchasing account.
